{"id":254709,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/10/维权网-湖北汪俊芳等人北京乞讨被关久敬庄毒打/","date":"2012-10-03T04:19:40Z","modified":"2012-10-03T04:19:40Z","title":"维权网 | 湖北汪俊芳等人北京乞讨被关久敬庄毒打（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员蒋正义报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日下午</span><span>，湖北省在京</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>位上访维权者到北京繁华商业街王府井乞讨，被警方抓进久敬庄关押遣送时，汪俊芳在久敬庄内被地方进京抓访人员打得头破血流，嘴里也不断吐血，报警不出警，汪俊芳被强行架走。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据一同行乞的湖北省十堰市上访维权者尹登珍、周大珍、冷新芳说，与她们一起到王府井行乞的上访维权者汪俊芳，是湖北省武汉市东西湖区人，因上访反映承包土地被非法征用，而被政府报复关押黑监狱</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">45</span><span>天，合法利益未解决，人身权又遭到更严重侵犯和身心伤害。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>她们都是因长期上访，导致经济生活极度贫困，绝望之中向路人乞讨，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>时</span><span>许，她们刚到王府井行乞，就被警方抓进东交民巷派出所询问，随后又送进久敬庄，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日中午，从武汉坐飞机赶到北京的抓访人员，见到汪俊芳后，对汪一阵暴打，头被打破，鲜血直流，嘴里也不停吐血，其他上访维权者赶忙不断向</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>报警，警方一直不出警，抓访人将汪俊芳架出久敬庄。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>湖北十堰市上访维权者尹登珍、周大珍、冷新芳</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>人在午后，被十堰市政府驻京办接出后释放，逃过了关黑监狱或押回当地的命运。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>上访维权者尹登珍因上访遭多次拘留，关精神病院、劳教和被控“敲诈政府罪”</span><span> </span><span>判刑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>年。尹登珍说，从我受害的亲身经历上，可以看到十堰市政府和公、检、法是违法犯罪分子的保护伞，是欺压百姓的暴力组织。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Kra25aQuhDk/UGusG7s1p8I/AAAAAAAAQQ8/6uXn8YxHl2M/s1600/%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E6%B1%AA%E4%BF%8A%E8%8A%B3.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Kra25aQuhDk/UGusG7s1p8I/AAAAAAAAQQ8/6uXn8YxHl2M/s320/%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E6%B1%AA%E4%BF%8A%E8%8A%B3.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>汪俊芳</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Ze49Yg8x2sY/UGusIr_L-XI/AAAAAAAAQRE/bdMWtdBQExU/s1600/%E4%B9%9E%E8%AE%A8%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E5%86%B7%E6%96%B0%E8%8A%B3.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Ze49Yg8x2sY/UGusIr_L-XI/AAAAAAAAQRE/bdMWtdBQExU/s320/%E4%B9%9E%E8%AE%A8%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E5%86%B7%E6%96%B0%E8%8A%B3.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>冷新芳</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-D970t_DcCLc/UGusJ1wv8PI/AAAAAAAAQRM/BwhUL73Eauo/s1600/%E4%B9%9E%E8%AE%A8%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E5%B0%B9%E7%99%BB%E7%8F%8D.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-D970t_DcCLc/UGusJ1wv8PI/AAAAAAAAQRM/BwhUL73Eauo/s320/%E4%B9%9E%E8%AE%A8%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E5%B0%B9%E7%99%BB%E7%8F%8D.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>尹登珍<span> </span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-lY9vl2Z44sU/UGusLwPfc0I/AAAAAAAAQRU/CJK8X_foqhg/s1600/%E4%B9%9E%E8%AE%A8%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E5%91%A8%E5%A4%A7%E7%8F%8D.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-lY9vl2Z44sU/UGusLwPfc0I/AAAAAAAAQRU/CJK8X_foqhg/s320/%E4%B9%9E%E8%AE%A8%E8%AE%BF%E6%B0%91%E5%91%A8%E5%A4%A7%E7%8F%8D.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>周大珍</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-74878